tea

Class TeaBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • tea.TeaBase

  • public abstract class TeaBase
extends java.lang.Object
    Base object provides useful methods to support describing tests. When you create your own test class, it has to be exteded from this class. 
     
 public class YourTest extends tea.TeaBase {
     ...
 }
